trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode" /> to remove.
trans-unit.target: 要移除的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode" />。

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified tree node from the tree node collection.
trans-unit.target: 从树节点集合中移除指定的树节点。

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode> is removed from the tree node collection, all subsequent tree nodes are moved up one position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode>从树节点集合，所有后续的树节点将上移集合中的一个位置删除。

trans-unit.source: Enumerating the collection and removing nodes is not supported.
trans-unit.target: 不支持枚举集合和删除节点。
